  "unmapped_findings": [
    "Figure 1 shows OIM-EBSD results of the three alloys in HR + CR condition with colored IPF, IQ and phase contrast maps.",
    "Figure 2 shows XRD patterns of 28Mn0Ni and 15Mn5Ni alloys in HR + CR and heat-treated conditions.",
    "Figure 3 shows OIM-EBSD results of the three alloys in HR + CR + 1023 K condition.",
